- Added support for validating Microsoft Entra v2 access tokens during Windows MDM enrollment. Configure your Entra application client IDs under `mdm.windows_entra_client_ids` (Settings > Integrations > MDM > Microsoft Entra, or GitOps `controls.windows_entra_client_ids`) so that on-premises MDM applications created in Entra after 2026-07-01, which issue v2 tokens whose audience is the application client ID, can enroll. v1 tokens continue to work unchanged.
